Welcome to Relax Resort

Escape the Ordinary at Our Hawaiian Hotel
​

Packages

Pamper Package 

How long has it been since you treated yourself to a little “Me Time”? Sneak away to the Relax Spa and let our therapists indulge you with a replenishing facial, mani-pedi and the therapeutic body treatment of your choosing. 
​​LEARN MORE​
BOOK NOW

Dinner on Us Package

You select the setting for your private dinner: in one of our oceanfront restaurants, on your private balcony or under a palm tree on the beach. We’ll take care of the rest, including picking up the check. 
​LEARN MORE
BOOK NOW

Oceanside suite

These beautifully appointed suites are steps from the beach and infinity pool and offer views of the resort’s tropical trees and shrubs. Each suite has been furnished in a contemporary coastal style and all feature a master bedroom with a King bed and a separate living area with a sofabed. 
LEARN MORE
BOOK NOW

CONDÉ NAST TRAVELER

"It’s like they created a little corner of paradise – just for you."

Guest amenities

signature dining

Savor award-winning dining in three distinctive settings, where the ambiance and ocean breezes are as fresh and inspiring as the cuisine. 

relax spa

Escape the worries and stress of daily life at the luxurious Relax Spa. Here, the rhythm of the tides and an easygoing Island vibe welcome you to heal and replenish with a pampering massage, facial or body treatment.

wedding services

From intimate family affairs to grand ballroom celebrations, our experienced wedding team specializes in designing fully customized weddings with no detail overlooked. 
It’s daybreak at Relax Resort in Kailua-Kona, Hawaii. The sun glitters across crystalline Pacific Ocean waters, rolling onto a powdery ribbon of private, white sand beach. Sleek, contemporary architecture and décor are beautifully framed by manicured tropical landscapes, brilliant gardens and fifty-foot palms.
 
Think of Relax Resort as just the Hawaii you have come to discover: The gentle tides of one of Kailua-Kona’s best swimmable beaches, perfect for snorkeling, surfing or splashing among mild-mannered Hawaiian monk seals. Elegant dining at our Upscale Restaurant, a chic, modern eatery with panoramic ocean views. The sparkling waters of an infinity pool that seem to disappear into the Pacific surf beyond.
 
Escape, unplug and reconnect with what’s truly important in life at Relax Resort. 

Location

Overlooking a private white sand beach in a quiet area of Kailua-Kona, Relax Resort feels worlds apart from civilization yet just moments from it all: delightful historic sites, charming shopping, splendid oceanfront restaurants and, of course, exhilarating watersports.
